    "title": {
      "rendered": "5 Ways the Internet of Things Could Transform Fundraising"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Internet-of-Things-Nonprofits-Fundraising-Facebook.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19729\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-19729\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Internet-of-Things-Nonprofits-Fundraising-Facebook-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"Internet of Things Nonprofits Fundraising Facebook\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Internet-of-Things-Nonprofits-Fundraising-Facebook.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Internet-of-Things-Nonprofits-Fundraising-Facebook.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Internet-of-Things-Nonprofits-Fundraising-Facebook.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Internet-of-Things-Nonprofits-Fundraising-Facebook.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Internet-of-Things-Nonprofits-Fundraising-Facebook.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Internet-of-Things-Nonprofits-Fundraising-Facebook.jpg?w=770&amp;ssl=1 770w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>By the year 2020, over 26 billion things\u200a\u2014\u200acars, appliances, roads\u200a\u2014\u200awill be connected to the Internet. Known as the <strong><a class=\"markup--anchor markup--li-anchor\" href=\"http://www.informationisbeautiful.net/visualizations/the-internet-of-things-a-primer/\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-href=\"http://www.informationisbeautiful.net/visualizations/the-internet-of-things-a-primer/\">Internet of Things</a></strong>, our digital and philanthropic lives are about to transform. In the coming years the social good sector will launch <strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/IoT\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#IoT</a></strong> apps that\u00a0will empower real-time giving while watching TV or listening to radio through your refrigerator. These new fundraising apps will use new payment systems, such as\u00a0<strong><a href=\"http://www.samsung.com/us/samsung-pay/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Samsung Pay</a>\u00a0</strong>and\u00a0<strong><a href=\"http://www.apple.com/apple-pay/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Apple Pay</a>\u00a0</strong>(or\u00a0your Facebook or Twitter login), and fundraising will transcend to level never even imagined by <strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Jetsons\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Jetsons</a></strong>.</p>\n<hr />\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\">1) Household Appliances</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/5-Samsung-Family-Hub-Refrigerator-Announced-in-CES-2016-with-Large-Display-1.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19732\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19732\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/5-Samsung-Family-Hub-Refrigerator-Announced-in-CES-2016-with-Large-Display-1.jpg?resize=600%2C320\" alt=\"5-Samsung-Family-Hub-Refrigerator-Announced-in-CES-2016-with-Large-Display-1\" width=\"600\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/5-Samsung-Family-Hub-Refrigerator-Announced-in-CES-2016-with-Large-Display-1.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/5-Samsung-Family-Hub-Refrigerator-Announced-in-CES-2016-with-Large-Display-1.jpg?resize=300%2C160&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2><em><strong>Imagine:\u00a0</strong></em>A breaking news story flashes on your refrigerator screen with an option to finger scan an <a href=\"http://www.wfp.org/emergencies/syria\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">urgent donation to a community in need</a>.</h2>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\">2)\u00a0Automobiles</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Tesla-Apps-P90D-Touchscreen.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19734\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19734\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Tesla-Apps-P90D-Touchscreen.jpg?resize=600%2C320\" alt=\"Tesla-Apps-P90D-Touchscreen\" width=\"600\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Tesla-Apps-P90D-Touchscreen.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Tesla-Apps-P90D-Touchscreen.jpg?resize=300%2C160&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Imagine:</em> Listening to your local public media during a pledge drive and <a href=\"http://www.npr.org/stations/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">signing up to become a monthly sustainer</a> through voice recognition while driving.</h2>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\">3) Smart TVs</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/SmartPay_TV_Main_1.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19736\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19736\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/SmartPay_TV_Main_1.jpg?resize=600%2C320\" alt=\"SmartPay_TV_Main_1\" width=\"600\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/SmartPay_TV_Main_1.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/SmartPay_TV_Main_1.jpg?resize=300%2C160&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Imagine:</em> Watching an evening news segment about the poaching crisis in Africa and pointing\u00a0your remote (or smartphone) at the screen to easily <a href=\"http://www.blackmambas.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">donate to an anti-poaching unit</a>.</h2>\n<h1>4) Public Space Advertising</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/maxresdefault.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19739\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19739\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/maxresdefault.jpg?resize=600%2C320\" alt=\"maxresdefault\" width=\"600\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/maxresdefault.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/maxresdefault.jpg?resize=300%2C160&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2><em>Imagine:</em> Waiting for your morning bus and being able to <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fiJsV54m9xI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">add your name to a petition or donate to an awareness campaign</a> through <a href=\"http://nfc-forum.org/what-is-nfc/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">near field communication</a>\u00a0on an ad screen at the bus stop (or subway, airport, etc.).</h2>\n<h1>5) Smartwatches</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/apple-watch-left-hand.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19740\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19740\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/apple-watch-left-hand.png?resize=600%2C320\" alt=\"apple-watch-left-hand\" width=\"600\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/apple-watch-left-hand.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/apple-watch-left-hand.png?resize=300%2C160&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2><em>Imagine</em>: <a href=\"https://support.twitter.com/articles/20172678\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Checking your Twitter</a> on your smartwatch while on a walk and being able to easily donate to your favorite nonprofit on Twitter by simply tapping a <a href=\"https://cash.me/cashtags\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">$Cashtag</a> in a tweet.</h2>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><em>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</em></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-16024\" style=\"margin: 10px; border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mobile-for-good-look-inside.jpg?resize=99%2C150\" alt=\"mobile for good look inside\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" /></a>Based on more than 20 years of experience and 25,000+ hours spent utilizing mobile and social media, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><strong>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</strong></em></a> is a comprehensive 256-page book packed with more than 500 best practices. Written on the premise that all communications and fundraising are now mobile and social, Mobile for Good is a step-by-step how-to guide for writing, implementing, and maintaining a mobile and social fundraising strategy for your nonprofit.</p>\n",
